properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const baseW = thisLayer.effect('Greaser Creaser')('Upper Width') * thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0];const w = baseW + thisLayer.effect('Greaser Creaser')('Outline Width') * (thisLayer.effect('Greaser Creaser')('Auto-scale') == 0 ? 1 : thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0]);const l = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}').effect('Limber System')('ikfkfreeksides')[1] * thisLayer.effect('Greaser Creaser')('Split') * 0.01;const rnd = thisLayer.effect('Greaser Creaser')('Rounding') * 0.01;const fac = 0.5523;const verts = [	[w*0.5, 0],	[w*0.5, -l],	[0, -l + w * rnd * 0.5],	[-w*0.5, -l],	[-w*0.5, 0],]const intans = [	[0,0],	[0,0],	[w * 0.5 * fac, 0],	[0, w * 0.5 * fac * rnd],	[0,0],]const outtans = [	[0,0],	[0, w * 0.5 * fac * rnd],	[-w * 0.5 * fac, 0],	[0,0],	[0,0],]createPath(verts, intans, outtans, false)

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const w = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Joint Group').content('Arm Circle').content('Arm End').size[0];const l = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}').effect('Limber System')('ikfkfreeksides')[1];const strkW = content('Limb').content('Joint Group').content('Arm Circle').content('Stroke 2').strokeWidth;createPath([	[w*0.5, -l],	[w*0.5, -strkW],	[-w*0.5, -strkW],	[-w*0.5, -l],], [], [], false)

properties.name: Size
properties.expression: const baseW = thisLayer.effect('Greaser Creaser')('Upper Width') * thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0];const w = baseW + effect('Greaser Creaser')('Outline Width') * (thisLayer.effect('Greaser Creaser')('Auto-scale') == 0 ? 1 : thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0]);[w, w * Math.abs(thisLayer.effect('Greaser Creaser')('Rounding')) * 0.01]

properties.name: Scale
